name: slurmpter
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "slurmpter" %}
{% set version = "1.0.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: a4dd1eeb5692ce2e92847fb01e73430323c912c3132d53418f0bd1f0ea5dcd34

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.5
  run:
    - graphviz
    - pycondor
    - python >=3.5

test:
  imports:
    - slurmpter
    - slurmpter.slurm
    - slurmpter.job

about:
  home: "https://github.com/isaac-cfwong/slurmpter"
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "A package to build Slurm submit files of a workflow of jobs easily."
  doc_url: https://slurmpter.readthedocs.io
  dev_url: https://github.com/isaac-cfwong/slurmpter

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - isaac-cfwong
